{"tid":1759590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你做選民嘅快啲入嚟登記做選民啦","createTime":"2019-11-27T17:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T06:19:46.000Z","uid":223741,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2100ca2b988bf41149733e86ddbb5bd4ba325a67","tid":1759590,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:49:40.000Z","msg":"好快就2020年啦<br />\n2020年9月就立法會選舉<br />\n到時有兩張票可以投票<br />\n雖然未必個個接受到呢個制度<br />\n但作為一個可以表態嘅機會<br />\n中聯辦不停叫人登記做選民做鐵票嘅時候<br />\n各位係時候盡一分力登記做選民<br />\n用選票向共產黨說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面會講點樣做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3455dcecaf599ac6d2d6768a3644c09e2e95fcc2","tid":1759590,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"呢？"},{"pid":"c63c2d47c0ee642562ba8806184b295c2b4a2423","tid":1759590,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"我睇唔明佢個符合資格係咩意思，我申請左做地區選民，但係我唔係功能界別嘅人，我係咪無資格去參與立法會同埋超級區議會選舉投票。"},{"pid":"a63d87a48d7429c8604783bfd151dcec9975a4fd","tid":1759590,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63c2d47c0ee642562ba8806184b295c2b4a2423","tid":1759590,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"我睇唔明佢個符合資格係咩意思，我申請左做地區選民，但係我唔係功能界別嘅人，我係咪無資格去參與立法會同埋超級區議會選舉投票。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"正常會做埋超級區議會嘅選民"},{"pid":"3c1ef4b631fe88e9449bd93dd948b7830b55bed6","tid":1759590,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63d87a48d7429c8604783bfd151dcec9975a4fd","tid":1759590,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63c2d47c0ee642562ba880618